   http://www.oorexx.org/license.html

Installation:
   See INSTALL file

Changes:
   See HISTORY file

Requirements:
   * A version of Rexx that supports use of extension libraries.
   * Version 7.8 (or later) of the freely available cURL distribution
     available from http://curl.haxx.se

